Package: jakpoststyle
Title: R Package to Apply The Jakarta Post Custom Theme to Datawrapper Charts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Dzulfiqar",
           family = "Fathur Rahman",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "frdzulfiqar@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Edit Datawrapper chart properties using 
    a custom theme of The Jakarta Post. This makes it easy to position the y-axis
    on the right side, modify the y-axis elements, write the byline, 
    add the Post's logo and create a COVID-19 annotation.
